## Component Diagram
```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "Frontend Components"
        Pages["Pages (Home, Login, etc.)"]
        Widgets["Widgets"]
        Providers["State Management"]
        Models["Data Models"]
    end

    subgraph "Backend Components"
        Handlers["HTTP Handlers"]
        Auth["Authentication"]
        Database["Database Layer"]
        Middleware["Middleware (CORS, Logger)"]
        Utils["Utilities"]
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        WebTester["Web Tester Service"]
        SiteChecker["Site Checker"]
    end

    Pages --> Widgets
    Widgets --> Providers
    Providers --> Models
    Handlers --> Auth
    Handlers --> Database
    Handlers --> Middleware
    Handlers --> Utils
    Utils --> WebTester
    Utils --> SiteChecker
```
